580
01:06:28,084 --> 01:06:29,051
lt's me.

581
01:06:29,051 --> 01:06:30,746
l'm gonna tell you something.

582
01:06:30,886 --> 01:06:33,548
l've seen an awful lot of you
in the last few days.

583
01:06:33,656 --> 01:06:36,591
l'd just as soon change shoes
with you right now.

584
01:06:37,793 --> 01:06:39,488
That's right.

585
01:06:40,029 --> 01:06:42,964
You want to know why? 'Cause you've
got a girl that loves you.

586
