who didn't want me to
come down here?

591
01:07:00,249 --> 01:07:01,511
She hates me, too.

592
01:07:02,818 --> 01:07:05,343
l've never been a success at
anything l've tried to do.

593
01:07:05,421 --> 01:07:08,356
