all. A plain old failure.

594
01:07:09,892 --> 01:07:11,757
But l'm not going to be, this time.

595
01:07:12,061 --> 01:07:14,291
l'm going to make this one. l'm
going to do this right.

596
01:07:14,563 --> 01:07:17,299
That's the reason you're going
back to stand trial.

597
01:07:17,299 --> 01:07:19,233
Because of me. You understand?

598
01:07:19,935 --> 01:07:20,867
Because of me.

599
