Kid, wake up.

602
01:08:12,154 --> 01:08:13,883
Kid. Look at me.

603
01:08:16,559 --> 01:08:18,220
You know that man?

604
01:08:18,861 --> 01:08:20,351
He's a bad man.

605
01:08:21,564 --> 01:08:23,293
He wants to hurt me.

606
01:08:23,866 --> 01:08:26,198
You wouldn't want that, would you?

607
01:08:27,336 --> 01:08:28,268
Now look.

608
01:08:44,787 --> 01:08:45,719
Easy.

609
