Don't listen to him, kid.
Bring it to me.

616
01:09:05,508 --> 01:09:07,442
Hear what l'm telling you.
Drop it.

617
01:09:09,745 --> 01:09:10,677
Bring it back.

618
01:09:11,147 --> 01:09:12,079
Drop the gun.

619
