Yeah?

624
01:09:34,904 --> 01:09:36,303
Kid, come back.

625
01:09:56,058 --> 01:09:57,259
What's wrong with you,
running away?

626
01:09:57,259 --> 01:09:59,193
You should get your
bottom smacked!

627
01:09:59,728 --> 01:10:02,663
Don't you know you might have
been caught by the lndians?

628
01:10:07,603 --> 01:10:11,004
l didn't mean to slap you,
back there. l'm sorry.

629
01:10:13,475 --> 01:10:15,409
Will you forgive me, please?

